            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-white p-3 rounded mb-3">
            <p>In certain situations, a team approach can be beneficial. However, I am not a supporter of a fully facilitated approach where individuals are confined to a room singing campfire songs. I do believe that everyone should be engaged and included in the process. The involvement of the entire team is crucial, but I prefer a more dynamic approach rather than simply sitting in a room and discussing every detail. It is essential to have someone experienced leading the team effectively. Thank you for considering these points.</p>
            <ul class="post-meta mb-0">
                <li class="post-date"><i class="uil uil-calendar-alt"></i><span>16-07-2024</span></li>
